data.description: Come take a closer look at this wonderful Redlands home situated on almost 1/3 acre lot w/ mature landscaped yard & plenty of room for everyone & everything!!! This 4 bed, 2 bath, oversized 2 car garage home features 2 living areas & tons of upgrades throughout. Upstairs boasts an open living/kitchen & dining making the space very functional for entertaining & there is a deck right off the kitchen into the backyard.  There are also 2 beds & a bath upstairs & 2 beds & a bath downstairs as well as second living area with a cozy wood burning stove on newer platform. Laundry is located in the spacious mudroom that connects to garage. Beautiful yard w/ trees, storage shed, RV Parking & more. Great neighborhood, close to trails for hiking & biking...Move in ready & waiting for new owners!!
